quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  95,1,Ndahiye igiti cy’umutini n’icy’umuzeti
  95,2,N’umusozi wa Sinayi
  95,3,N’uyu mujyi utekanye (Maka)
  95,4,Mu by’ukuri twaremye umuntu mu ishusho nziza
  95,5,Hanyuma tuzamushyira mu rwego rwo hasi cyane (ageze mu zabukuru atagishoboye kugira icyo yimarira)
  95,6,"Uretse babandi bemeye bakanakora ibikorwa byiza (n’iyo bageze mu zabukuru, hari ibikorwa byo kwiyegereza Imana bakomeza gukora); abo bazagororerwa ibihembo bidashira (Ijuru)"
  95,7,"None se nyuma y’ibyo (yewe muntu), ni iki kigutera guhakana umunsi w’ibihembo"
  95,8,Ese Allah si We Mucamanza usumba abandi
  96,1,Soma ku izina rya Nyagasani wawe waremye (ibiriho byose)
  96,2,Yaremye umuntu mu rusoro rw’amaraso
  96,3,Soma! Kandi Nyagasani wawe ni Nyirubuntu uhebuje
  96,4,We wigishije (umuntu kwandika) akoresheje ikaramu
  96,5,Yigishije umuntu ibyo atari azi
  96,6,Oya! Mu by’ukuri umuntu ararengera (arahakana kandi agakora ibibi)
  96,7,Iyo amaze kubona ko yihagije (kubera ibyo atunze)
  96,8,Mu by’ukuri (umenye ko) kwa Nyagasani wawe ari ho garukiro
  96,9,Ese (yewe Muhamadi) wabonye wa wundi (Abu Jahl) ubuza
  96,10,Umugaragu (wacu Muhamadi) kugaragira
  96,11,Ese (yabuza ate umugaragu wacu) aramutse ari mu nzira y’ukuri
  96,12,Cyangwa ari gukangurira (abantu) kugandukira Allah (mbwira icyaba iherezo ry’umubuza)
  96,13,Ngaho mbwira (Abu Jahl) aramutse ahinyura (ukuri) akanatera umugongo
  96,14,Ese ntabwo azi ko Allah abona (ibyo akora)
  96,15,"Oya! Natarekera aho, tuzamufata uruhanga rwe turukururire mu muriro"
  96,16,"Uruhanga rubeshya, rw’urunyabyaha"
  96,17,Ngaho nahamagare abambari be
  96,18,Natwe tuzahamagara abamalayika bacu barinda umuriro (kugira ngo bamukanire urumukwiye)
  96,19,"Oya! (Yewe Muhamadi), ntukamwumvire (Abu Jahali), ahubwo ujye wubama (usali) uniyegereze Allah"